{"tid":1299629,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主黨吳思諾：青年發展委員會應降低委員年齡要求","createTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T08:31:44.000Z","uid":2617,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0e8d4c7b7a377ae6357787e631ebc63c88c208e2","tid":1299629,"uid":2617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥表示，會全面改革諮詢委員會的模式，其中青年發展委員會將會大幅改變組成和運作模式。<br />\n<br />\n青年發展委員會委員之一、民主黨吳思諾建議加入民主元素，一人一票選出青年代表，組成新的委員會。<br />\n<br />\n吳思諾又建議，參與人士的年齡可由12至35歲，實際操作需要再討論。她舉例說，委員會主席、政務司司長張建宗已經60多歲，不少委員亦都已不年青，既然政府想聆聽年輕人意見，應該降低年齡要求。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">咁就比人帶左風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你Ｄ委員會根本就係林鄭用黎轉移視線既野<br />\n咁都有人同佢討論呢Ｄ垃圾野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"a561b4244a2c9ccf5de6cbaa3163c6e584bd815c","tid":1299629,"uid":827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5817f2def72d43adbd9b2f0d0edf306fb7831124","tid":1299629,"uid":137459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:28:38.000Z","msg":"《一日爭取唔到真普選，我地永遠處於被動》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1299151\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1299151</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"297b1186ed80e801421c2cf0048bdefbd6cd85cb","tid":1299629,"uid":268019,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T08:30:20.000Z","msg":"你唔準咁講吳思諾 BB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c3fd9ae0377e2461079fbbbe8cb0e97a0119d4f","tid":1299629,"uid":276002,"like"